snippet.title: CoasterMania - Official Mixed Reality Trailer | Upload VR Showcase 2023
snippet.description: Watch the new trailer for CoasterMania, the physics-based VR game that lets you build your dream rollercoasters. With its new mixed reality update, players can now construct and view rides in their own home. CoasterMania's mixed reality update is available now on Meta Quest App Lab.
